::Shadow Wing::

She had been with the Preds and the crates outside the ship. Right 
then and there she was wishing Lunarpine was with her.  Right now, 
she was the only Maximal stadning infront of a group of Preds. She 
felt like getting the heck out of there, but she had to protect the 
ship.  
"Thank you for bringing the Energon.  Now I bid you all good day."

She opened her link, "I could use some help bringing in these crates" 
as she tapped into the ship intercom.
